snippet.title: TheRcKiwis
snippet.description:
TheRcKiwis are all about RC adventures! Here you will find everything from RC Bashing, speed runs to "How to" and review videos with everything in between.
 
We do not shy away from the big jumps and always on the lookout for new locations all around the world for filming some great content for you guys! We listen to our viewers and do the best we can to provide the content you want. So please never shy away from commenting we read all our comments and if you ever have a questions we will answer it as best we can!

We maybe small at the moment but I know that with your support we can grow and continue to test out new RC's that you guys want to see! So please let us know what RC's you're interested in and that could be in an upcoming video and we will  be sure to acknowledge you in it!

So what are you waiting for! Hit the Subscribe button and bell so you're notified on our next video!

Website: www.therckiwis.com
Facebook: The Rc Kiwis.
Instagram: @therckiwis

Thank you!
TheRcKiwis
